{"tid":207334,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓夜晚係咁叫，求救","createTime":"2017-04-18T22:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T08:11:02.000Z","uid":97409,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11d8aeeb689b87cee135eccbc48effc3e0da82ba","tid":207334,"uid":97409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:34:41.000Z","msg":"隻貓第一日拎返屋企，日頭唔叫，一到左夜晚不斷叫，比佢搞到訓唔到，有咩方法可以解決。就癲"},{"pid":"9d94bda5dac0b0c87e5d6b0f4acffb0f3e93efc8","tid":207334,"uid":46241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:45:45.000Z","msg":"比佢入房同你一齊訓 <br />\n我果隻養左8年都係夜晚叫<br />\n最近終於放左佢入房 天下太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25f967bde3fc66a9c508582df837566c6f0a76a","tid":207334,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:50:43.000Z","msg":"習慣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養得貓就預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8244dcbe095d8a742c66864cbed07bc176cf80f6","tid":207334,"uid":97409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比佢入房同你一齊訓 <br />\n我果隻養左8年都係夜晚叫<br />\n最近終於放左佢入房 天下太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但屋企人成日話唔衛生"},{"pid":"e0c2a86df70da170636eab796863d7072d0c8a5b","tid":207334,"uid":5426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比佢入房同你一齊訓 <br />\n我果隻養左8年都係夜晚叫<br />\n最近終於放左佢入房 天下太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但屋企人成日話唔衛生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓好乾淨 佢掛住你先叫你"},{"pid":"4672690bd7d0aac482f8be2235ff9bbaea6afb9e","tid":207334,"uid":97409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習慣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養得貓就預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係因為驚影響到屋企人，同嘈到鄰居。<br />\n所以想睇下有冇方法可以令隻貓夜晚唔好係咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc564466e4df350e79f393b0cc0660879b22f0e","tid":207334,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>習慣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養得貓就預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係因為驚影響到屋企人，同嘈到鄰居。<br />\n所以想睇下有冇方法可以令隻貓夜晚唔好係咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚計架喎<br />\n就算閹撚左佢 佢都係會叫春<br />\n習慣下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ae437b17cd13a4c43979fd9a4aacb798454f32","tid":207334,"uid":97409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T23:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>習慣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養得貓就預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係因為驚影響到屋企人，同嘈到鄰居。<br />\n所以想睇下有冇方法可以令隻貓夜晚唔好係咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚計架喎<br />\n就算閹撚左佢 佢都係會叫春<br />\n習慣下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3414c7a287b048b732582829648caf7faf9232de","tid":207334,"uid":97409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T23:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg&h=70d172e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻哀野真係好鬼得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b184093dccd706f9f71a2cc46088a1f91fc96c86","tid":207334,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"應該係驚 同未適應陌生環境 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我隻住左成個月都仲會嗌 不過你忍心唔理 佢就愈來愈少嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c616af03012bc564ae872d8e222eac43bca5a7dc","tid":207334,"uid":61987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg&h=70d172e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻哀野真係好鬼得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會訓係貓砂上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f651c107f728b0278af0062df7ed9e0c82f0565","tid":207334,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg&h=70d172e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻哀野真係好鬼得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會訓係貓砂上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a161afddf6e25d09dfcc9a16de9f1611f27a1fd5","tid":207334,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg&h=70d172e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻哀野真係好鬼得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會訓係貓砂上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4612588e9cf8fd429888d25ae84b543908da21","tid":207334,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c74716968e5e2e8fc105eac975eee3791fd9c350","tid":207334,"uid":12839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:32:20.000Z","msg":"正常架。未慣新環境<br />\n不過佢點叫你都要忍心唔理佢，唔係佢會覺得 叫=有人理，唔理佢 等佢叫到累就會自己收皮 <br />\n過一排就唔會叫"},{"pid":"c44558a1dbd69ae187b9acd1b9d9b2f60937506f","tid":207334,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"過多幾日習慣左就唔會叫得咁密<br />\n我主人第一日跟我返屋企搞到成家無得訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33261e622654825353d8f91b51cd36a04104a9a3","tid":207334,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F073454_fad8351c4d5280fdcd75b1986fefb95c.jpg&h=70d172e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻哀野真係好鬼得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會訓係貓砂上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未習慣新環境，覺得陌生，貓砂有佢啲貓味，瞓係貓砂盤聞住自己嘅味有安全感啲"},{"pid":"296d256d30b69052b32444023057d99c8c6d12de","tid":207334,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/21/105536_400def9a0dc405d74fc26404d5c90d7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F21%2F105536_400def9a0dc405d74fc26404d5c90d7e.jpg&h=f7e9fd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我女兒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭一個禮拜佢係好不安，你只要多啲陪佢唔好離開佢，佢就好快適應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e597563c764b4188446c22d69e65330bbaea1e6","tid":207334,"uid":93674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"我隻衰仔第一日返黎原本好驚，之後已經係咁撩我玩，玩足成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/21/122321_1407691184ffe21a59fcc3a4567df4cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F21%2F122321_1407691184ffe21a59fcc3a4567df4cc.jpg&h=e1494dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過多排就無事 佢再叫你就唔好理佢  等佢知道呢個方法唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fd10353ad88e14bfc18f82daa779ca52e5d0c1","tid":207334,"uid":97409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"比佢嘈左三日，終於自己頂唔順訓左<img src=